# Zig level definitions

# this file is case sensitive
 
# Amoeba - blobby thing, homes in on player, divides when shot.
# Flanker - tries to fly around behind player, then shoots in for the kill.
# Grunt - mindlessly moves toward player
# HeavyThing - invincible, gains speed when shot
# Obstacle - non-moving flashing square to annoy player
# Pacman - ...wackawackawacka...
# Rock - asteroids-style rock
# Snowflake - pretty snowflake
# Tank - homes in on player whilst firing
# UFO - asteroids-style UFO
# WallHugger - moves around edge of arena, firing inward.
# Wiggler - Wiggles toward player
# Zipper - Moves in straight line, periodically picks a new random direction
# ZipperMat - generates Zippers
# Invader - An invader. Possibly from space.
# Snake - Multi-segmented homing snake
# MineLayer - Mine-laying dude
# FatZapper - Green and mean, fires a big energy beam
# EdgePuller
# Divider - double-beam thingy
# Agitator - gets mad when you shoot it

LEVEL
